  "title": "Field Technician (6 months contract)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Field Technician (6 months contract | extendable)</strong><br /><strong></strong><br /><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Support installation and commissioning of smart lighting and control systems.</li><li>Perform testing, diagnostics, and troubleshooting for wiring, devices, and connectivity.</li><li>Assist in system integration with sensors, controllers, and software.</li><li>Maintain site reports and documentation.</li><li>Coordinate with project teams and ensure safety compliance on-site.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>ITE or Diploma in Electrical/Electronics/Related field.</li><li>Basic understanding of electrical circuits and wiring.</li><li>Ability to read electrical drawings.</li><li>Strong problem-solving skills and willingness to travel for field work.</li><li>Familiarity with LED drivers, sensors, and control protocols (DALI, 0–10V, Zigbee).</li><li>Basic networking knowledge is a plus.</li></ul>",
